   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n029_crew_kevin-1" image="QN_NPC_Engineer_Hubert.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Kevin$<BR>Oh, thank you thank you THANK YOU! Airship Engineer Hubert was next to me, so go talk to him. Maybe he'll tell you something he won't tell me, since you're both old.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1" image="QN_crew_kevin.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-a" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Did you see the thief?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>I heard Kevin call me old, that little... What's his problem?<BR>(You explain about the ring.)<BR>Oh, is that it? I thought he lost some toy of his. No wonder! He wouldn't shut up about that ring after you brought it back.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-b" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Then...it could have been the wind, right? Maybe he dropped it?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>Nope. I didn't see a thing!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-b" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300066" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-c" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Airship Engineer Hubert...what was in that bucket?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>(He looks around the area.) ...I don't think so. Looks like there was someone here, and they knocked over this bucket when they were trying to get away.<BR>(Airship Engineer Hubert shows you an overturned bucket. There is a powerful, disgusting, familiar smell on it...)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-c" image="QN_Npc_Woman_Trader_May.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-d" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I can't believe you bought this...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>This? May came by with something she said was really nice, just for me. It smelled like a dead, wet fluffalo, but it was cheap, so I bought it. Thought maybe I could use it for engine fuel or something.<BR>(You timidly sniff the bucket again, and gag. It's definitely the Nutritious Food.)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-e" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Where do they lead?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>It was cheap! Anyway, that thief hit this bucket hard. He must be covered in the stuff... Hey, footprints! (Airship Engineer Hubert points at some foul-smelling steps in the grass.)</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-e" image="QW_16.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-f" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Think I'll take your word for it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>Looks like... (Airship Engineer Hubert squints into the distance.) Ah, I think they trail off towards the Temple of the Sleepers. You might want to follow your nose, but I'm pretty sure that's where they lead.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n099_engineer_hubert-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Airship Engineer Hubert$<BR>I'll send word for the guards to be on the lookout, but these tracks are fresh. The thief should still be at the Temple!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
