   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n029_crew_kevin-2" image="QW_16.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Kevin$<BR>Huh? You're really gonna follow the thief to the Sleepers' Temple? Cool!<BR>Kick his butt and find my dad's ring!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
